Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to cope with the \Nturbulent Great Pirate Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}50 leaders hold the World Conference\Nevery four years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Known as the Reverie, it is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The times are changing drastically now.{\i0}
